{
  "stem": "26728.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and to be-- to be the victim as well as to be both the person who was sick enough to do that and the person who was too sick to get away were equally-- that must have been equally mortified by the fact that they couldn't control what was happening at all.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It just happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there's probably 200 men in this-- in this section of barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, let me get finished with the people because that was-- was really interesting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- and I didn't participate in any of that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they took them all through the camp, and they-- and they walked them back, marched-- escorted with soldiers with bayonets on them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the, the, the Americans were never-- I never saw any-- well, let me start-- I'm getting ahead of myself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was tremendous rage, but there was controlled rage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody yelled or spit on these-- even the inmates, these civilians, they just let them go by.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody said anything to them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When they were-- they wal-- they escorted back down the road toward Weimar, and there was a lieutenant that was in charge, a young infantry lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Somebody laughed, a woman or some women or some girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't hear this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But here they come again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He turned them around when he heard this laughter, and said, we're going to go back through that camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they took them back, and they took another tour of the same damn thing they had been through before with these soldiers with the bayonets.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they left the camp, and then there was no laughing on the second.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, I saw this, and Harry Herder-- the man that's on the internet at this Library of the Holocaust-- tells about this.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
